  sender: Developers
  subject: THANKS FOR PLAYING
  message: "Hello!! Dev\u2019s here. You\u2019ve reached the end of the game. Wahoooo!!!
    This game was made to fulfill our final requirements. We were given the theme
    telecommunications so we created our own analog horror universe, while using
    the Home Safety Hotline format because it is such a cool concept. Anyways,this
    was a ton of fun to make, but we aren\u2019t sure we will continue production.
    Nonetheless thank you so much for playing!!! "
